title: Barbed wire machine US-CS-A
title_uz: Tikanli sim ishlab chiqarish uskunasi US-CS-A
title_ru: Оборудование для производства колючей проволоки US-CS-A
short_description: Barbed wire is used to protect crops and similar areas from livestock and other objects. This US-CS-A equipment serves to produce exactly such barbed wire at a speed of 20 meters per hour. The equipment has a motor power of 2.2 kW and a total weight of 1200 kg. The equipment has two different dimensions: the first is 1950*950*1300 mm, the second is 1760*550*760 mm. The description includes other models of the equipment, and their prices and parameters differ from each other.
short_description_uz: Ekin maydonlarini va shunga o'xshash joylarni chorva mollari hamda boshqa narsalardan himoya qilish uchun tikanli simlardan foydalaniladi. Ushbu US-CS-A uskuna aynan shu kabi tikanli simlarni soatiga 20 metr tezlikda ishlab chiqarish uchun xizmat qiladi. Uskuna motor quvvati 2.2 kW va umumiy vazni 1200 kg. Uskunaning ikki xil o'lchamli shakllari bor: birinchisi 1950*950*1300 mm, ikkinchisi 1760*550*760 mm. Tavsifda uskunaning boshqa modellari ham aks etgan va ularning narxlari hamda parametrlari bir-biridan farqlanadi.
